Services Offered: GRE Coaching , SAT Coaching , GMAT Coaching ,
Details: Jamboree is the oldest institute in India and the best of its kind, which offers comprehensive classroom preparation programs for tests such as GMAT, GRE, SAT, TOEFLTM and IELTS. Jamboree centres are present in 14 cities of India and in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and Kathmandu . Each centre follows a uniform curriculum and has outstanding faculty, all of whom are trained in our head office. Each centre offers the same teaching standards and syllabus.At Jamboree, the most trusted name in India for education abroad, we help you give shape to your career and dreams. Founded in 1993, Jamboree attempted to fill the information gap on education abroad. Back then, the only information available on education abroad was through friends and family living or studying abroad. Thus, only a small percentage of interested students had access to information. Jamboree attempted to fill this information gap. Now when we in 'Team Jamboree' reflect on the past few years, we see thousands of our students on the thresholds of careers that would not have been possible without the right guidance at the right time.Jamboree, known for its thorough research and professionalism, is a one-stop shop for education abroad.Jamboree makes the entire process of studying abroad, from preparing to actually joining a foreign university, a smooth process. In recent years, the inclusion of several value-added services such as discounted couriers, educational loans and pre-departure orientation has made Jamboree Education Pvt. Ltd. a one-stop solution centre for all your study abroad requirements.

Our main goal is to train the students in design field which can help them to establish themselves in the current competitive market.. We train employees to satisfyingly fulfill the requirement of their employer. People with many professions and occupations approach us for the solutions as they trust our quality & its deliverance manner. This is the reason, we are not just a training institute but we also deals in corporate trainings, services, colleges and project outsourcing too.
Mission to start this organization is to provide quality engineers and services to the specific industries. There are lots of job requirements in the engineering design field, but students are not able to establish themselves according to the industrial requirements due to the lack of industry specific knowledge. There is big gap between knowledge that a fresh engineer acquire and industrial requirements. We work as a bridge between these two people by grooming the fresh students according to the industrial requirements with the help of various training programs. We involve our students in various live projects, so that they can understand the current trend of market. We believe in quality deliverance. We do not believe in just imparting software knowledge to our students, but we prepare complete packages to get settled up and create a new workbench in the market. To motivate and to encourage our students we train them well for interviews, client dealing skills, personality development etc. Our vision is to provide quality training and designing services to our clients and establish ourselves as one of the premiere training and service providers in the field of Engineering.

We implement a pedagogy called Peer Instruction that reduces teacher dependence and enables collaborative learning. Students consume lecture content in the form of recorded videos and reading material before attending class. In place of conventional lectures, classroom time is used to get students to work collaboratively on problem sets and clarify doubts by interacting with subject experts.
